entries.abort: That's right! Get out of here, pirate.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Stand by. This is a rich shipping lane. A freighter full of cargo will be by shortly.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Ok, there it is. Capture it and send it back to Dantooine. I will have another ship to meet it on this side.
entries.capture_complete: Capture process completed. Escort ship to jump coordinates.
entries.capture_phase_1_1: Blasted pirates! The CorSec are going to hear about this.
entries.capture_phase_1_3: Why don't you pirates get a real job?
entries.capture_phase_1_4: So, do you really think you will get away with this?
entries.capture_phase_1_5: Piracy is a capital offense in this region. You will be caught.
entries.capture_phase_2_1: Fine, I will do whatever you want me to...just don't destroy me.
entries.capture_phase_2_2: Ok, I will go to Dantooine.
entries.capture_phase_2_3: You might have captured me but you will pay.
entries.capture_phase_2_4: Dantooine? Fine...but you will pay for your crimes.
entries.capture_phase_2_5: I will go to Dantooine but I assure you I will escape once I get the chance.
entries.complete: Ok, I will go to Dantooine, but I am not doing this out of my own free will.
entries.failed_destroy: Blast it! We need those supplies, not scrap metal.
entries.failed_escape: You let it get away? I thought you said you were a good pilot.
entries.panic_1: What are they doing? Those incompetent fools...
entries.panic_2: Hey, I am not with him! Shoot him, not me!
entries.panic_3: Great...the CorSec would rather have me destroyed then fall into pirates hands.
entries.panic_4: I don't believe this. They have no clue what they are doing.
entries.quest_disable_d: Target the freighters engines and get them to come to a complete stop.
entries.quest_escort_d: Follow the freighter until it reaches a jump point to the Dantooine system. Protect it from CorSec who might try to get involved.
entries.quest_location_d: The station wants you to raid the shipping lanes of Corellia.
entries.quest_recover_d: Move in close to the freighter and wait for them to surrender.
entries.recovery_success: Good work. We will have our people on this side escort that freighter the rest of the way. There are more ships waiting to be captured if you want to do that again.
entries.target_disabled: The freighter has shut down it's engines. Move in close and wait for it to surrender.
entries.taunt_1: You will cease your current illegal activity immediately.
entries.taunt_2: You are in violation of Corellian law. Prepare to be destroyed.
entries.taunt_4: Pirates like you deserve no mercy.
entries.taunt_5: We will not allow you to have the freighter.
entries.thanks_1: Well, I guess I am stuck with you.
entries.thanks_2: CorSecs are nearly as bad as you pirates.
entries.thanks_3: I don't know who is worse...you or them.
entries.thanks_5: If I stay with you, they will blow me up. If I try to escape, you will blow me up. This stinks!
entries.title: Corellia System: Capture Cargo Freighter's Duty
entries.title_d: The Dantooine station needs supplies. They are willing to do anything to get those supplies, even support piracy. You are to raid the rich shipping lanes of Corellia and send the captured freighters to Dantooine.
